{"tid":9824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Angelababy曝兒時萌照 「從小美到大」破整形傳言","createTime":"2016-11-28T17:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T17:29:51.000Z","uid":9890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5407646eba86797411229e6b279b22b557c40de","tid":9824,"uid":9890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕「Angelababy」楊穎與黃曉明結婚1年，做人成功，自宣布懷孕消息以來，令粉絲又驚又喜，相當期待baby的出生，她今日在IG分享兒時照，更讓粉絲大嘆：「從小美到大！」<br />\nAngelababy目前已懷有5個月身孕，樂當稱職人妻，今日在IG開心的大曬兒時嫩照，讓大批粉絲看的大呼「超级可爱」，照片中，Angelababy綁著2束馬尾，稚嫩的臉蛋相當可愛，比起一旁同年的小朋友，個頭來的高出許多，有愛的牽著一旁的妹妹，模樣相當萌，讓不少粉絲看了直誇「從小美到大」、「真的從小就好看」，更有粉絲大呼「破了整容輿論」，表示Angelababy自曝兒時照，根本間接破先前整形一說，大力挺偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/1898730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1898730&d=IaM7PEbqaTm0p1rdo6owMcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=1f14eac4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1898730&h=1547b22a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/1898730</a>"},{"pid":"2de56370ecc7f9a70385cdb4687405961aaaa61c","tid":9824,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"c0984ce5922c7b14f42bbcdccaa7ab7e5e66385e","tid":9824,"uid":5990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的"},{"pid":"86eb1baa921ca061513aa2173e659d555551979c","tid":9824,"uid":16499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的"},{"pid":"3b461719d757cf89c9f14ae9ad0e66e2b818be9c","tid":9824,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n名"},{"pid":"b33c2f29c7